{"tid":86772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★［投票］假如支那同日本開戰，只是第二次甲午戰爭，支那會全軍覆沒！","createTime":"2017-01-19T10:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T14:49:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c94f2b9cc4b7de0da11b06c5ff4f0676ebc2ca53","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:16:40.000Z","msg":"認同         正評<br />\n<br />\n不認同     負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e860dad1b156e9109b57d5d4b6ca868bcb3b6a","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VPaILKYcl-o/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FVPaILKYcl-o%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=4b5ffea7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4667b27a64dfcea6cac357f9de4b78a09585ae40","tid":86772,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fa950771df0986b66344922a7bda66cc41d3880","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"1． 昧於情勢：清廷官員多以為洋務運動有成，並輕視日本的實力，以為中國兵力足懲日本。此外，李鴻章始誤<br />\n<br />\n信俄國之相助，終失望於英、美二國之調停。當權者對國內、國外之情勢掌握不了，中國自處下風。<br />\n<br />\n2． 政策不一：清廷對日本入侵朝鮮之意見分歧，也是戰敗的因素。德宗主戰，李鴻章主和，慈禧則拿不定主<br />\n<br />\n意，認為「戰比和好」，既開戰而無決心。於是，日本大軍進逼之際，清廷始倉惶備戰，故戰事一敗塗地。<br />\n<br />\n3．軍備廢弛：洋務運動所練新軍，多紀律敗壤，且士氣低落。另外，多年營建的艦隊，由於資金不足，裝備殘<br />\n<br />\n缺，戰鬥力不足。加上，慈禧挪用海軍經費來修築頤和園，亦影響了海軍實力。於是，一經接戰，海陸軍俱<br />\n<br />\n敗於日本。應戰的北洋艦隊已是四洋海軍中實力最強者，但無論火力、噸數、航速等仍比不上日本聯合艦隊<br />\n<br />\n，故此終敗於日本之手。<br />\n<br />\n4．指揮失誤：當時中國陸軍不相統屬，且將帥不和，教於朝鮮及遼東戰場屢嚐敗績。北洋海軍於黃海一役失利<br />\n<br />\n後，傷亡慘重，又坐困威海衛內，不出應戰，亦使日本得以從容圍攻，最後全遭消滅，國防盡失。<br />\n<br />\n5．政治腐敗：清廷政治腐敗，貪污成風，政出多門，任用私人。另外，清廷內部出現派系鬥爭，各派不能協調<br />\n<br />\n，故事權不能統一，政治混亂不堪，作戰亦自然失敗。"},{"pid":"70ecfe714628baf4713fc6ecba7ed7fc032d585f","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"所有甲午戰敗原因全match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ad458fca066f6c31d912dde3330ffcd3cda401","tid":86772,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"103397f06e848047831ec5811730fa04a30eb814","tid":86772,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"老實講如果冇美國撐腰日本未必贏<br />\n<br />\n講州際導彈，大陸有東風射程一萬公里一支十彈頭，日本一支都冇<br />\n<br />\n加上日本自己未有能力研發反導技術，始終要靠美國撐腰"},{"pid":"bea94dce04bee322814f36eff17eafe6006777f2","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img11.itiexue.net/1411/14117423.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg11.itiexue.net%2F1411%2F14117423.jpg&h=6ed5e1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題為傷得不輕的豬：上圖說得是中日甲午海戰，清軍大敗。下圖是列強在圍觀一身穿清兵服裝，傷痕累累，拖著長尾巴無路可走的豬。"},{"pid":"07ccc1cae606e730ad92229081632d8458291086","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img4.itiexue.net/1411/14117428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.itiexue.net%2F1411%2F14117428.jpg&h=86e3817c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題為厚面皮：滿清官員的大頭木質厚臉已經被日本兵刨掉了一半，出醜於天下了。"},{"pid":"12c199267978f821747160eac0f0e28bfed9f705","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img7.itiexue.net/1411/14117431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg7.itiexue.net%2F1411%2F14117431.jpg&h=e3517d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題為膽小鬼之舞：上圖是諷刺滿清官員顧前不顧後，以致被日本人從後攻佔了炮臺。下圖是打了敗仗的滿清官員依舊歌舞昇平。"},{"pid":"4550146efb0e01bca6afac73c33ebc3aeb867e54","tid":86772,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講如果冇美國撐腰日本未必贏<br />\n<br />\n講州際導彈，大陸有東風射程一萬公里一支十彈頭，日本一支都冇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加上日本自己未有能力研發反導技術</span>，始終要靠美國撐腰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本唔係無技術無能力，只係因為安保同戰後條約一直限住日本既軍事發展，唔可以有進攻型既軍備研發"},{"pid":"2dbbbc3057b7d5fdb4c4f1dc363735843e576a52","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img4.itiexue.net/14117416_1000_1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.itiexue.net%2F14117416_1000_1000.jpg&h=ac8b0587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾個日本兵堆個雪人就嚇得清兵屁滾尿流，跪地求饒。"},{"pid":"f4019b35b76397cc6aa3f94df8cb7cc8f1321ce2","tid":86772,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老實講如果冇美國撐腰日本未必贏<br />\n<br />\n講州際導彈，大陸有東風射程一萬公里一支十彈頭，日本一支都冇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加上日本自己未有能力研發反導技術</span>，始終要靠美國撐腰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本唔係無技術無能力，只係因為安保同戰後條約一直限住日本既軍事發展，唔可以有進攻型既軍備研發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n反導並不算進攻型軍備<br />\n<br />\n但日本係導彈技術、全球定位技術始終比較落後<br />\n<br />\n舉個實例，呀支那自己有套叫「北斗」既全球定位系統，依家上面好多汽車導向由GPS轉左做北斗，皆因比較平<br />\n<br />\n可惜日本始終冇能力研發全球定位系統，要靠美國GPS"},{"pid":"b8d9150e13d170f360873719b90b9c8e0b42806f","tid":86772,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"強國唯一可以贏既就係等人地打佢領土，只後慢慢消耗對方既軍力，不過而家既中國仲邊有價值比人入侵"},{"pid":"25a10aa4654fe22fafea5df549566edbbadcc8bf","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"662cbcecea9e1376ce4d61817419da5593d1f5c2","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6492feaa92048dbd493db55d487bd9ff11f033","tid":86772,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T19:19:51.000Z","msg":"唔會，日本無能力反攻大陸，最後支那只會賠錢，然後對外宣傳戰勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f91d5014a9284f3b65738269a79da2656f80cc","tid":86772,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐"},{"pid":"1b00367233f2f4c7794f8ac0d1165426f2b878f7","tid":86772,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國戰勝，香港又有咩好結果???"},{"pid":"a33866640c9ab546c8eeb2b77087bad7d8698cb4","tid":86772,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國戰勝，香港又有咩好結果???</blockquote><br />\n中國戰勝關香港乜事 香港咩事都無 <br />\n相反 如果中國戰敗 香港點會立足到姐 軍隊又冇 地方細人口少 資源缺乏"},{"pid":"b21c1f1b5b85d6dc6747ba05bd7b4227d31ffd34","tid":86772,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T20:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國戰勝，香港又有咩好結果???</blockquote><br />\n中國戰勝關香港乜事 香港咩事都無 <br />\n相反 如果中國戰敗 香港點會立足到姐 軍隊又冇 地方細人口少 資源缺乏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國戰勝左，即係支那模式係work, 你仲想過你高等華人自由生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻送你去新土地開發啦，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb0c09628fd54092e1f6169178e76040b3a6c27","tid":86772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐</blockquote><br />\n再一次 馬關條約，再被割讓，香港win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d356dc10bf41c98ac893c2c422394d2b5da95fb7","tid":86772,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"咩<br />\n日軍偷襲運兵船<br />\n慈禧大后挪用軍費<br />\n<br />\n好多強國人仲講緊呢d <br />\n覺得甲午戰爭輸得唔抵<br />\n再打多次 都只會輸<br />\n<br />\n好多支國人仲唔明 甲午戰爭完全無運氣成份<br />\n<br />\n清朝係將領，戰略，戰術，軍備，後勤全方面崩敗<br />\n好像甲午戰爭時 日軍已經有護理，救護系統<br />\n<br />\n買多幾隻軍艦有撚用<br />\n陸軍<br />\n仲係果個不停得個跑字的葉志超"},{"pid":"4a2941f91cd6e9454c0bf96d4cdc06a4b1cf03e3","tid":86772,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實中國如果戰敗，香港會有咩好結果姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國戰勝，香港又有咩好結果???</blockquote><br />\n中國戰勝關香港乜事 香港咩事都無 <br />\n相反 如果中國戰敗 香港點會立足到姐 軍隊又冇 地方細人口少 資源缺乏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國戰勝左，即係支那模式係work, 你仲想過你高等華人自由生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻送你去新土地開發啦，on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國戰勝 咪 趁有威勢 順勢 食左香港，台灣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46c8abc42532fb753df3f8637cd9e090857f273","tid":86772,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:53:04.000Z","msg":"今時今日既中國無可能輸俾日本啦   核武啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   日本有無先？"}]}